#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Marketing Automation </font></strong>,"
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email Marketing</font></strong>,"
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Social Media Marketing </font></"
"strong>, and <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS Marketing </font></"
"strong>."
msgstr ""
"Gestiona todos tus canales de comunicación desde un solo lugar con las "
"aplicaciones <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Automatización de "
"marketing </font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Marketing "
"por correo electrónico</font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Marketing social</font></strong> y <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Marketing por SMS</font></strong> de Odoo."

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting App</font></"
"strong>)"
msgstr ""
"Gestiona tu contabilidad con mayor facilidad gracias a un entorno "
"completamente integrado. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Contabilidad</font></strong>)"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your team's and integrate them in all processes by adding "
"the<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Employees App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Gestiona a tu equipo e intégralo en todos los procesos desde la aplicación "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Empleados</font></strong>."

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Move or reschedule the appointment (the patient is notified automatically)"
msgstr ""
"Mueve o vuelve a programar la cita (el paciente recibe una notificación "
"automática)"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to manage your entire "
"business from your phone."
msgstr ""
"Odoo está totalmente integrado en una aplicación. Descárgala para gestionar "
"todo tu negocio desde el móvil."

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo te ofrece infinitas posibilidades, tales como:"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Esto es solo un resumen de las funcionalidades incluidas en este paquete. "
"Añade nuevas aplicaciones, elimina o modifica los datos de demostración y "
"prueba todo lo que tiene para ofrecerte."

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once an appointment is booked, you can see it in the <strong>Calendar App</"
"strong>."
msgstr ""
"Una vez reservada una cita, podrás verla en la aplicación "
"<strong>Calendario</strong>."

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model:crm.stage,name:physical_therapy.crm_stage_6
